ZH: 我们将在这片开阔地扎营。
EN: We will set up camp in this open field.

ZH: 明天我们会扎营在山脚下。
EN: Tomorrow we will camp at the foot of the mountain.

ZH: 我们要找个合适的地方扎营。
EN: We need to find a suitable place to set up camp.

ZH: 他们在森林里扎营度假。
EN: They are camping in the forest for vacation.

ZH: 今晚我们将在河边扎营。
EN: Tonight we will camp by the river.

ZH: 他们决定在海滩上扎营。
EN: They decided to camp on the beach.

ZH: 大家快点，我们要在天黑之前扎营。
EN: Hurry up, we need to set up camp before it gets dark.

ZH: 队伍决定暂时扎营休息一下。
EN: The team decided to set up camp and take a rest.

ZH: 明天我们将继续前进，今晚在这里扎营。
EN: We will continue our journey tomorrow, and camp here tonight.

ZH: 找到水源是扎营的第一要务。
EN: Finding a water source is the first priority when setting up camp.

ZH: 在这片草地上扎营是个不错的选择。
EN: Setting up camp on this grassland is a good choice.

ZH: 他们带上了帐篷和睡袋，准备扎营。
EN: They brought tents and sleeping bags, ready to set up camp.

ZH: 扎营的地方要远离野生动物的活动区域。
EN: The campsite should be far away from the activity areas of wild animals.

ZH: 扎营需要好好规划才能确保安全。
EN: Proper planning is necessary to ensure safety when setting up camp.

ZH: 扎营之前要检查周围是否有危险品。
EN: Check for hazardous materials around before setting up camp.

ZH: 我们需要用篝火烧热食物和水，要先扎营再做。
EN: We need to set up camp before starting a fire to heat up food and water.

ZH: 他们决定扎营在海拔较高的地方，以避免蚊虫。
EN: They decided to set up camp at a higher altitude to avoid mosquitoes.

ZH: 扎营时要注意保护环境，不要破坏自然资源。
EN: When setting up camp, be mindful of protecting the environment and not damaging natural resources.

ZH: 天气不好，我们只能临时扎营在树林里。
EN: The weather is bad, so we can only temporarily set up camp in the woods.

ZH: 扎营需要合作和沟通，才能顺利完成任务。
EN: Setting up camp requires cooperation and communication to successfully complete the mission.
